{"tid":485831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同大家分享一件火車上既事","createTime":"2017-12-01T09:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-02T12:56:35.000Z","uid":80344,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b54a5d3a8500e812164b189ae91d8af136854ff","tid":485831,"uid":80344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:48:29.000Z","msg":"今日答火車返屋企個陣 上車見到有個智障人士係到哇哇叫啦 咁大家正常都離佢遠小小 佢就企係車門到邊叫邊風景 架車都幾多人 我同個女同學就企係佢隔離 以防萬一我仲用身企中間擋住 <br />\n<br />\n係呢個時候 大家都知火車有個位係有透明玻璃 有個媽媽帶著個bb坐左係到 同個智障只有一塊玻璃之隔<br />\n<br />\n個智障見到個bb就突然覺得好得意 係咁笑同做動作 <br />\n個bb都見到佢 正以為可能會大哭一場個時<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個bb笑得好開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個智障都笑得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個畫面真係對我有個好大既衝撃 唔知大家明唔明啦 不過好想分享下 人大左就唔單純 對任何事都充滿戒備啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30fbb79d49ff6b1b69714e371c5b5b458bbba8c2","tid":485831,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba43b938bb59299c64f18eba7dea8dceeaace375","tid":485831,"uid":125460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cda9740cd937ee606b062fd5647bfd82190036","tid":485831,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"8b38c7b1889cc8a1b054558289459f312057c10e","tid":485831,"uid":85307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T09:57:44.000Z","msg":"教育問題 污名化太勁"},{"pid":"3c6a7dde73dffb68f09b571d05ac7ae0ac2a4d86","tid":485831,"uid":88256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"明你想講咩 同之前某張種族歧視嘅圖類似 白人bb拖住黑人嘅手"},{"pid":"9ef4a92427eea521daf6f5aab0e6af845182d2e3","tid":485831,"uid":531,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T10:01:54.000Z","msg":"個b對住佢笑就冇事啫，對住佢喊個智障會唔會扯火拍玻璃大叫你唔知"},{"pid":"4735fb35f58af8f00f80c7de3061f20c0f82b12e","tid":485831,"uid":80344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個b對住佢笑就冇事啫，對住佢喊個智障會唔會扯火拍玻璃大叫你唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都岩既 不過見到咁有感而發"},{"pid":"72afbfeb8b6194ec699634e0cbebe7152183a60a","tid":485831,"uid":26380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:33:15.000Z","msg":"其實弱智人士冇惡意"},{"pid":"36675b809fba2f72c03256e0b958474ea278ae10","tid":485831,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:52:57.000Z","msg":"純真"},{"pid":"422a6401ca39a39d2e912bae22e9d12ce49c5ac9","tid":485831,"uid":60238,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T18:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實弱智人士冇惡意</blockquote><br />\n佢地控制唔到，萬一出事你又追究唔到佢地，咁唯有保持距離，冇計<br />\n如果佢整到既係你屋企既小朋友/老人家，睇你仲會唔會咁講<br />\n<br />\n我樓下有個弱聽+弱智，牛高馬大，廿幾三十歲<br />\n試過有次同lib，佢想同另一個小朋友打招呼，就笑住大大力拍佢個頭，跟住個細路喺度喊，個細路老豆就鬧鳩佢，個弱智又聽唔明<br />\n但其實佢對住個個都會咁，只不過識佢既都知佢唔識就力，同埋大家成年人識擋/避<br />\n<br />\n好似呢種人，你教又教唔到佢，佢屋企人又唔理，你除左避開仲可以點?"},{"pid":"dfa33d710363db8f418e05dbeb05763b8d87e5e3","tid":485831,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T19:05:37.000Z","msg":"智障同有暴力傾向應該唔同既"},{"pid":"b388f5a002fb5d86e41c23a8774a796a093f4c23","tid":485831,"uid":80344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}